The paper describes the creation of an open-source simulation based on an existing Dutch liveability score with a built-in AI module. The use of AI and simulation platforms suggests that the paper could belong to the sub-categories of Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI), Computational Engineering, Finance, and Science (cs.CE), Cybersecurity (cs.CY), Social and Information Networks (cs.SI), and Machine Learning (cs.LG).
